The paper focuses on image hashing, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach utilizes deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it aims to improve retrieval accuracy for image datasets.
